IEnumerable<bool> OpenSim.Region.ScriptEngine.Shared.YieldProlog.Functor2.unify ( object  arg  ) 

If arg is another Functor2, then succeed (yield once) if this and arg have the same name and all functor args unify, otherwise fail (don't yield). If arg is a Variable, then call its unify to unify with this. Otherwise fail (don't yield).

Implements OpenSim.Region.ScriptEngine.Shared.YieldProlog.IUnifiable.
